posting_body: ['We are just seven minutes from downtown Minneapolis, yet it feels like living in the country!', "Situated on over six acres, surrounded by woods, you'll enjoy peace and serenity.", 'Rent $1585 includes underground heated parking space, heat, and trash.', 'You pay electric, water, sewer, internet, and cable', '2nd  floor, corner unit', 'Kitchen has electric stove with self-cleaning oven, dishwasher, refrigerator and garbage disposal', 'Tons of closet space', 'Bath and a half', 'Large living room 21 x 12', 'Master bedroom 17.8 x 11.7 half bath off master', 'Bedroom 12.4 x 11.6)', '* Nonrefundable application fee is $40/ adult (all adults must apply)', '*$200 holding deposit due at the time of application', '* Jetty deposit Move in without the high up-front costs or deposit is equal to one months rent', '* We do Credit Checks * must have satisfactory Rental History', '* Income: Gross monthly income (before taxes) must be 2.5 times the monthly rent.', '* We do Criminal Background Checks.', "*Rental applications may be subject to GOLDMARK'S criminal criteria", 'Visit us on our website at <URL>.', 'You can view and apply for all available units at <URL>.', 'show contact info']
